title: Fitness Center, 24hr. Emergency maintenance, New LED Lighting
posting_body: Orchard Ridge has interiors matching your style.
All our one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans are embellished with contemporary features that add to your convenience.
These include in-unit washers & dryers, private balconies, and wood-burning fireplaces.
We also provide amenities answering your needs.
Every time you come home you will be greeted by many opportunities to relax.
From basking in the sun to challenging your muscles, there is something for everyone to do.
Orchard Ridge is near everything you want.

Found right off 164th St SW, with quick access to Highway 99 , I-5, and future Lightrail, our community is the perfect starting point for your daily adventures at Alderwood Mall or 11 minutes from Paine Field.
This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 838 Sq.
- Easy Access To I-5 and I-405 Interchange
Pet Fee $300.00 per pet, Pet Deposit $250.00 per pet, Pet Rent $40.00 per pet.
